N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 2 ยง 101.6 - Report to comptroller

State Regulations

The amount remaining after such deduction shall be remitted
forthwith to the State Comptroller accompanied by a report in such form and
detail as the State Comptroller may prescribe. Notes
